  <brief_title>Subclassification of the Syndrome of Inappropriate ADH Secretion</brief_title>
  <official_title>Subclassification of the Syndrome of Inappropriate Antidiuresis Via Copeptin - What is the Genesis of ADH-independent SIADH?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
